{
  "text": "The combination of fibrotic lesions and emphysema has been classified into 2 groups: diffuse forms of fibrosis with emphysema, and localised forms of fibrosis with emphysema [CITATION_1] . AEF [CITATION_2] , SRIF [CITATION_3] , and RB-ILD with fibrosis [CITATION_4] are categorised as localised forms, and Katzenstein et al. and Yousem suggested that SRIF and RB-ILD with fibrosis are not a diffuse fibrosing interstitial pneumonia. Kawabata et al. reported that AEF could be included as part of the spectrum of SR-ILD [CITATION_5] ; however, no correlation with radiological features has been reported thus far.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "26240034",
